- Overload alerts.
#### Implementation Ideas
Resource calculators with math libs.

### Story Points Estimation
#### Detailed Description
Estimate effort with points.
#### How It Works
1. Assign points to stories.
2. Use in velocity calculations.
3. Planning poker integrations.
#### Sub-Features
- Custom scales (Fibonacci).
- Group estimation.
#### Implementation Ideas
Custom fields for points.

